BuildRequires:    R-devel >= 3.1.0
Requires:         R-core >= 3.1.0
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-stats 
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-matrixStats 
Requires:         R-stats 
Requires:         R-CRAN-matrixStats 

%description
Filter CpGs based on Intra-class Correlation Coefficients (ICCs) when
replicates are available. ICCs are calculated by fitting linear mixed
effects models to all samples including the un-replicated samples.
Including the large number of un-replicated samples improves ICC estimates
dramatically. The method accommodates any replicate design.

